Seattle; Gordon H. Russell, Hale Center, Texas; Danine A. Rydland,
Martinsburg, W.Va.; Roland K. Sanchez, Belen, N.M.; James L. Scott,
Washington D.C., and Marcia Shoup, La Grande, Ore.
   The 18 were selected from among more than 150 candidates.
   The committee is expected to hold its first meeting in September.
