   Chairman and Chief Executive Officer: Lee Iacocca.
   U.S. plants and other facilities: 46, including 21 in Michigan.
   Plant closings: 17 since 1979, including 11 in southeast
Michigan. Six additional closings planned between September 1988
and September 1989.
