   Kaisertech Ltd., which said its directors appointed a committee
to consider a sale or buyout, jumped 2~ to 18.
   Cooper Cos. gained 2[ to 14}. The company said it would put each
of its principal businesses up for sale after the government
opposed its plans to sell its contact lens operations to
Schering-Plough Corp.
   On the downside, Learonal dropped 4{ to 16] on word that Asarco
