   Standard & Poor's industrial index fell 1.87 to 301.66, and
S&P's 500-stock composite index was down 1.53 at 258.79.
   The NASDAQ composite index for the over-the-counter market lost
2.11 to 379.51. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index closed at 302.39, down .15.
